channel.title: Admin Maker: Make yourself admin on almsot any server, WORKS
channel.description:
This is a little program that i created, it goes into servers into the cache files and if the server has admins in the file. If the server has it you get a free admin :) For it to work you need to make sure the server is up, go on cmd.bat and type admin (sevrerip) (port) logging in you need to use [eof], [character], or [account]. Post your feedback here. WARNING: ALL OWNERS OF SERVERS DO ::banuser [eof], ::banuser [character], and ::banuser [account] IF YOU DONT WANT PEOPLE MAKING THEIRSELVES ADMINS.
PS: This program HAS been tested by me and it works. scan it although i already did, and when u downmload something do not open it untill you scan it or your computer may be in risk from a trojan/virus. You do not want these.
Anyway this prgram has no virus/trojan so if you still want to scan you may. I was just putting important knoledge in your head :)
